#

Tuna Salad Sandwich

10 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

FishGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

Quick MealLunchSandwich

Description

A classic, refreshing tuna salad sandwich that's perfect for a quick lunch or snack.

Ingredients

  • canned tuna: 1 can (5 oz)
  • mayonnaise: 2 tablespoons
  • celery, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • red onion, finely chopped: 1 tablespoon
  • dill pickles, chopped: 1 tablespoon
  • bread (whole wheat or white): 2 slices
  • lettuce leaves: 2 leaves
  • tomato, sliced: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • mustard (optional): 1 teaspoon
